name: Golden Angle
description:
From the collection "Inside: lost Identity"

I am a dream bird
A legendary horse
Phoenix, unicorn, or maybe a mermaid ...
No, maybe not...
I'm a little golden angel
A Black Devil
Or a lonely god
Or maybe I'm a star
A sun
A moonlight
Or something more real
like this wind that blew and went
The day which became night
Or simpler
A look in Your Eyes
One step with your foot
A hand in your hand
Or that sound
In your ear
or even less
One moment, one second, a feeling ...
I am everything 
and I am nothing
